        <Parent_String>post-1945 architecture and design styles and movements [300111998], international post-1945 styles and movements [300022097], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
